      • unpackFilterInputStream

        public static InputStream unpackFilterInputStream(FilterInputStream is)
                                           throws IllegalAccessException
        Finds the underlying InputStream to a FilterInputStream. Note this is not always possible due to security restrictions of the JVM.
        Throws:
        IllegalAccessException - If security policies of the JVM prevent unpacking of the FilterInputStream.
